sequenceDiagram
    participant Op as Operator (Browser)
    participant SW as SetupFlow.svelte
    participant SS as SourceStep
    participant PS as ProviderStep
    participant AS as AuthStep
    participant API as Webshell API
    participant KC as macOS Keychain
    participant DB as SQLite (litellm_config)

    Op->>SW: Opens webshell (first run)
    SW->>SS: Renders SourceStep (step='source')
    Op->>SS: Clicks "Bring Your Own Key"
    SS->>SW: step.set('provider'), tier='byok'

    SW->>PS: Renders ProviderStep
    Op->>PS: Selects provider (e.g. Anthropic)
    PS->>SW: step.set('auth'), backend='anthropic', agent='lightarchitects'

    SW->>AS: Renders AuthStep
    Op->>AS: Enters API key
    AS->>API: PUT /api/auth/credential/anthropic/key {key}
    API->>KC: security add-generic-password -s la-anthropic-credential -w <key>
    KC-->>API: 200 OK
    API-->>AS: {ok: true}

    AS->>API: POST /api/setup/install_litellm {provider, base_url}
    Note over API: Phase 3 W3 deliverable
    API->>DB: session_store.save_litellm_config(base_url, model)
    DB-->>API: Ok(())
    API-->>AS: {ok: true, proxy_url: "http://localhost:4000"}

    AS->>SW: step.set('done')
    SW->>Op: Setup complete — copilot available
